Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:33.21,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:18.45,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,The clouds still shine white
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:27.13,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,In the blackness of the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:35.25,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,The red light of the fires...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it yourself that day: "Take apart a Simoun."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that's in there is a helix.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can understand about it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}do{\i0} see something! What? What are you seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:13.00,Titles,,0,0,0,,One By One
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What're those for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm collecting them to make a cradle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A cradle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Back where I grew up, we always used to put out cradles in the springtime. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're an offering to grant peaceful rest to the souls of those who died before their time. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's too thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what could have left her in that state, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Limone, it would be good for you to stay by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of all of us, you're the one closest to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril, did anything happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We were unable to find the enemy base ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why they've gone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing else happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, what was it that Dominura saw? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We should not have touched such sacred things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I should not have touched them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish. I'll never let you touch them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You should rest till tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Dominura is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've sighted the enemy at 11 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't seem to be attacking, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret to say that she remains indisposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril is exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in no condition to pray right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,With Dominura unable to pray as well, for now you'll be taking orders from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"Orders?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like we're in the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're only continuing our reconnaissance. There's no reason for Neviril to go. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Aaeru just gave up back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was quite taken aback by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in the past she'd've dragged her off by the hand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bleah! I don't want to see Aaeru like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's cool because she's so positive that it's overbearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Being so weirdly considerate... it's totally not like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel that way about Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Limone, where's Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? I just saw her go outside, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what she could be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking that I'd take a shower or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No one asked you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know why you're apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just bowing your head for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault that you're feeling bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand why, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know it's because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare be so conceited!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Floe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That was {\i1}so{\i0} uncool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive my impertinence, Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was insolent of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuria and that girl. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She was never looking at {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru made me see the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To both of them I am just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a tool. A tool to take them "higher."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... I've made a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were with you—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the person you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say what I think you're going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...then I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...that my shell will break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not really yourself right now. So—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I say such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The air around here really stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The air?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay, Alti?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if Floe really wants to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina, Rodoreamon, back them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yun and the others haven't come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy isn't attacking, so to just go out without a plan like that—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I made a bad decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't always be by your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can still try to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to go look at the Simoun today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna play hide-and-seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kid stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it, Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Morinas, count to a hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be cheating on us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,1... 2... 3... 4... 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide, Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,6... 7... 8... 9... 10...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That song...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as Aaeru's music box!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Door to a New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the song of the migrants, who were searching for a land of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:15:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tempus Spatium took us in when we had been wandering without rest. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Chor Dextra was created to perform the Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We were warriors chosen in the knowledge that we would die...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I was fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange for my death, the Holy Land gave my life meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I always have. Always!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You are needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do the Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do it with you, Dominura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... you're my pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Paraietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain is getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, come back inside before it affects your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need to talk to Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I so indecisive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm like this, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, this is {\i1}very{\i0} weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's better to wait until Dominura comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying we can't do anything without her giving instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is no time to be petty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Petty," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if we keep on like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to pair with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I are going to go on a reconnaissance mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And from now on—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the one to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Morinas, you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril, no! You're still—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me go, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do about our game?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:19:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the eyes of someone who's about to die. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Limone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominura, I want to hear your advice on this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:21:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your judgement so unreliable that you'd rather listen to someone who's been asleep? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.53,0:21:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominura...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,More, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.97,0:21:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,By dismantling the Simoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel as though I saw what lies beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't know if you really saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Until you actually do it, you won't know for sure. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:22:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly seems like it, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.79,0:22:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You were always told to fly higher, weren't you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To draw Ri Maajons in the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So to deny you that would be to deny you your very self. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.49,0:22:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we're so much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and you chose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.90,0:22:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That connection is what creates the Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for you, I want to draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.94,0:22:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Emerald Ri Maajon.
